{"tid":2073072,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《黑社會檔案之黑金帝國》電影揭露港共鄉黑聯手犯罪電影","createTime":"2020-06-21T05:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T12:10:06.000Z","uid":129019,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1004412897d1b159dde4e01444e0e8e0410fb7c0","tid":2073072,"uid":129019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IXLE1wjXD0Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIXLE1wjXD0Q&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=ee5d77f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IXLE1wjXD0Q</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WWsMrEx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWWsMrEx.png&h=49187296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0wt0v6m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0wt0v6m.png&h=a6c68ad4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a71fbca7bdfe604545abdd4d335af7f6bcfaa93","tid":2073072,"uid":129019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cOa98Vq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcOa98Vq.jpg&h=c5b96474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新界某鄉市黑社會執委員會主席何權，獲悉特區政府準建設西鐵發展計劃事宜，確定沿線發展區域一帶，大量撥地興建丁屋，串謀某一派鄉事執委週甘銓、羅偉雄、梁召權、趙振明等人，進行非法行賄認定原居民，以厚利報酬而換取支持投票當選為主席，以便日後進身立法機關執法，好待以主席身份代表鄉民向特區政府商議土地收購索償。廉署高層幹部接獲此案，據案情涉及西鐵發展計劃，牽涉人仕甚廣，隨即成立項目小組調查此案，並設立代號為「西域黑金」行動。"},{"pid":"4b43c7c7434ae950c7a2b7f47b7b3e5d0e7a35c3","tid":2073072,"uid":129019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T06:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CdAx6WO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCdAx6WO.jpg&h=ca689092&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4eebc2f94a7ac4b9a4ac2ddb484c438384453451","tid":2073072,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"Documentary"}]}